      "rationale": "Experimental test conditions documented with calibrated flow loop at 37°C ± 0.5°C. Flow rate measured via Coriolis meter (±0.5% FS). Rotational speed verified with optical tachometer (±5 RPM). Inlet/outlet pressure measured with calibrated transducers. Bovine blood rheology characterized via cone-and-plate viscometry. All conditions replicated in CFD boundary conditions within measurement uncertainty."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
